title: AuCalc
description: A GPA and CGPA Calculator for Anna University
point1: A web app that helps to calculate GPA and CGPA for Anna University students.
point2: Mainly focus on Easy User Flow to make great User Experience.
point3: Tech used: React, TailwindCSS, Material UI, Axios, Router, Python, Django, Pandas, PostgreSQL.
